steps.name: Verify client can be deleted from UI
check via api that the simple client has been created
search a new client by phone number from UI
assert - search returns a one client in the UI

attachments.name: click on element and wait 30000ms for response OK
click on element and wait 30000ms for response OK
click on element and wait 30000ms for response OK

steps.name: search a deleted client by phone number from UI
assert - search returns a zero client in the UI
